sentences: Sina oled üheks meie parimatest mängijatest.
Praegu on ta üheks populaarsematest inimestest riigis.
context: 'Üheks' is used to denote that something or someone is 'as one of' a group. It's commonly used when listing an individual as part of a collective noun, like ranking or categorizing them within a larger set.
